n. Enkele belangrijke componenten en functies van Azure Security waarmee wij werken zijn Azure Security Center, Microsoft Entra ID, Azure DDoS Protection en Azure Sentinel.","Neem contact op voor meer informatie","Sugar Glaze",false,{"id":217,"name":218,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":19,"height":219,"formats":220,"hash":245,"ext":23,"mime":26,"size":246,"url":247,"previewUrl":18,"provider":58,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":248,"updatedAt":248,"documentId":249,"publishedAt":153,"focalPoint":18},779,"security azure.jpg",850,{"large":221,"small":226,"medium":232,"thumbnail":238},{"ext":23,"url":222,"hash":223,"mime":26,"name":224,"path":18,"size":225,"width":29,"height":62},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_security_azure_b1610cf1cb.jpg","large_security_azure_b1610cf1cb","large_security azure.jpg",107.3,{"ext":23,"url":227,"hash":228,"mime":26,"name":229,"path":18,"size":230,"width":20,"height":231},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_security_azure_b1610cf1cb.jpg","small_security_azure_b1610cf1cb","small_security azure.jpg",39.16,332,{"ext":23,"url":233,"hash":234,"mime":26,"name":235,"path":18,"size":236,"width":44,"height":237},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_security_azure_b1610cf1cb.jpg","medium_security_azure_b1610cf1cb","medium_security azure.jpg",71.35,498,{"ext":23,"url":239,"hash":240,"mime":26,"name":241,"path":18,"size":242,"width":243,"height":244},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_security_azure_b1610cf1cb.jpg","thumbnail_security_azure_b1610cf1cb","thumbnail_security azure.jpg",12.37,235,156,"security_azure_b1610cf1cb",150.42,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/security_azure_b1610cf1cb.jpg","2024-08-08T08:50:26.921Z","z3xlbivuior2upad6adbxjgz","global.alternating-page-section",{"id":252,"title":253,"subTitle":18,"content":254,"callToActionText":18,"callToActionLink":18,"colorStyle":255,"showAsides":215,"imageUrl":256,"__component":250},26,"Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS)","Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS) helpt bij het beheren van applicaties die in containers draaien. Het vereenvoudigt en automatiseert de implementatie, het beheer en de operationele taken van Kubernetes-clusters. Door gebruik te maken van AKS kunnen organisaties zich richten op het ontwikkelen en beheren van hun applicaties, terwijl Microsoft de complexiteit van de Kubernetes-infrastructuur beheert. Hierdoor kunnen organisaties hun software efficiënt, betrouwbaar en kosteneffectief beheren. Doordat onze experts ruime kennis en ervaring hebben met AKS kunnen ze de klanten op een juiste manier helpen.","White",{"id":257,"name":258,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":19,"height":219,"formats":259,"hash":280,"ext":23,"mime":26,"size":281,"url":282,"previewUrl":18,"provider":58,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":283,"updatedAt":283,"documentId":284,"publishedAt":153,"focalPoint":18},780,"containers.jpg",{"large":260,"small":265,"medium":270,"thumbnail":275},{"ext":23,"url":261,"hash":262,"mime":26,"name":263,"path":18,"size":264,"width":29,"height":62},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_containers_2e766510ad.jpg","large_containers_2e766510ad","large_containers.jpg",163.19,{"ext":23,"url":266,"hash":267,"mime":26,"name":268,"path":18,"size":269,"width":20,"height":231},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_containers_2e766510ad.jpg","small_containers_2e766510ad","small_containers.jpg",49.69,{"ext":23,"url":271,"hash":272,"mime":26,"name":273,"path":18,"size":274,"width":44,"height":237},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_containers_2e766510ad.jpg","medium_containers_2e766510ad","medium_containers.jpg",101.49,{"ext":23,"url":276,"hash":277,"mime":26,"name":278,"path":18,"size":279,"width":243,"height":244},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_containers_2e766510ad.jpg","thumbnail_containers_2e766510ad","thumbnail_containers.jpg",12.65,"containers_2e766510ad",240.51,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/containers_2e766510ad.jpg","2024-08-08T08:54:58.426Z","idshbfmg66aak9yxdr9d22c7",{"id":155,"title":286,"subTitle":18,"content":287,"callToActionText":18,"callToActionLink":18,"colorStyle":214,"showAsides":215,"imageUrl":288,"__component":250},"Infrastructure as Code (IaC)","Infrastructure as Code (IaC) is het beheren van een Azure cloud-omgeving door middel van code en softwareontwikkelingstechnieken om infrastructuur te automatiseren, te configureren en te beheren. Het biedt versiebeheer voor configuraties, wat samenwerking en terugkeer naar eerdere versies vergemakkelijkt. Bovendien zorgt IaC voor consistentie in verschillende omgevingen en maakt het schaalvergroting eenvoudiger door configuraties te herhalen zonder handmatige ingrepen. \n\nAls je vragen hebt of ondersteuning nodig hebt, kunnen de Azure Experts je alles vertellen over Infrastructure as Code.",{"id":289,"name":290,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":19,"height":219,"formats":291,"hash":312,"ext":23,"mime":26,"size":313,"url":314,"previewUrl":18,"provider":58,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":315,"updatedAt":315,"documentId":316,"publishedAt":153,"focalPoint":18},781,"infrastructure.jpg",{"large":292,"small":297,"medium":302,"thumbnail":307},{"ext":23,"url":293,"hash":294,"mime":26,"name":295,"path":18,"size":296,"width":29,"height":62},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_infrastructure_bf66532759.jpg","large_infrastructure_bf66532759","large_infrastructure.jpg",246.61,{"ext":23,"url":298,"hash":299,"mime":26,"name":300,"path":18,"size":301,"width":20,"height":231},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_infrastructure_bf66532759.jpg","small_infrastructure_bf66532759","small_infrastructure.jpg",69.57,{"ext":23,"url":303,"hash":304,"mime":26,"name":305,"path":18,"size":306,"width":44,"height":237},"https://incredible-bee